### 小程序登录
POST http://localhost:7878/user/appUser/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "demo-code",
  "nickname": "演示用户",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

### 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:7878/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123456"
}

### 商品列表
GET http://localhost:7878/user/product/list?page=1&size=10

### 商品详情
GET http://localhost:7878/user/product/1

### 商品 SKU
GET http://localhost:7878/user/product/1/skus

### 购物车列表
GET http://localhost:7878/user/cart/list
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 加入购物车
POST http://localhost:7878/user/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "skuId": 1,
  "quantity": 2,
  "checked": 1
}

### 创建订单
POST http://localhost:7878/user/order/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "receiverName": "张三",
  "receiverPhone": "13800138000",
  "receiverAddress": "上海市浦东新区",
  "remark": "demo订单",
  "items": [
    {
      "skuId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 管理端订单列表
GET http://localhost:7878/admin/order/list?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
